Package ui

Class InstructionsButton

java.lang.Object
ui.PauseButton
ui.InstructionsButton
public class InstructionsButton extends PauseButton
This class represents 1 Button on the Instructions GameState. A button will be linked to different GameStates so that the Game can change states based on what button is pushed.
Author:
Sean-Paul Brown
